# üöÄ **faiz** ‚Äî Your All-in-One Super Command-Line Toolkit

**faiz** is a powerful **command-line utility** designed to streamline your daily tasks‚Äîwhether you're a developer, tech enthusiast, sysadmin, or just someone who loves automation.

From image conversions and QR code generation to SSH management, project scaffolding, and comprehensive PDF operations, **faiz** puts everything you need right at your fingertips in one clean, easy-to-use command.

‚úÖ Fast ‚Ä¢ üó≠Ô∏è Secure ‚Ä¢ üîß Modular ‚Ä¢ üåê Internet-Ready ‚Ä¢ ‚ö° Productivity-Boosting

> **Note:** Currently, **faiz** is only supported on **Windows** systems.

---

## üì¶ Installation

### Install via **PyPI**

```bash
pip install faiz
```

üëâ **PyPI Package:** [https://pypi.org/project/faiz/](https://pypi.org/project/faiz/)

### Or Clone via **GitHub**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/zokasta/faiz.git
cd faiz
python setup.py install
```

üëâ **GitHub Repository:** [https://github.com/zokasta/faiz](https://github.com/zokasta/faiz)

