## ‚ú® Key Features Overview

| Feature                | Description                                                  |
| ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| ‚öôÔ∏è Environment Manager | Manage and edit `.env` files effortlessly                    |
| üñºÔ∏è Image Converter    | Convert images to **WebP**, **AVIF**, **JPEG**, **PNG**      |
| üîç Web Search          | Search instantly via Google or Microsoft Edge                |
| üîë SSH Manager         | Save, list, and connect to SSH profiles quickly              |
| üêô Git Automation      | Perform common Git operations faster                         |
| üì± QR Code Generator   | Generate QR codes from text, links, or data                  |
| üßÆ File Type Counter   | Count files by extension and size in any directory           |
| üëü Cursor Fun          | Move mouse cursor randomly for fun or screen awake scenarios |
| ‚öõÔ∏è React.js Setup      | Scaffold basic React.js projects quickly                     |
| üÑª Laravel Setup       | Bootstrap Laravel PHP projects in seconds                    |
| üìÑ **PDF Suite**       | Lock, unlock, merge, split, compress, rotate, watermark PDFs |

